What Should a Functional Consultant Understand?

Instead of memorizing the icons, understand which department uses which module.

| Department       | Odoo Module                                  |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| Sales            | CRM, Sales                                   |
| Purchase         | Purchase                                     |
| Warehouse        | Inventory                                    |
| Finance          | Accounting                                   |
| HR               | Employees, Recruitment, Attendance, Expenses |
| Factory          | Manufacturing, Quality, Maintenance          |
| Customer Support | Helpdesk                                     |
| Marketing        | Marketing Automation                         |
| Website Team     | Website, eCommerce                           |
| Administration   | Contacts, Calendar, Settings                 |


