=====

Odoo is not a single application; it is a collection of integrated business applications.
Each icon represents a business function or department.
Different departments work in their own modules, but all data is stored in one centralized database.
As an Odoo Functional Consultant, your role is to understand the client's business, 
identify which modules they need, configure those modules, and ensure they work together to support the company's processes.

